# Group Products

Product-related data.

## Product Types Collection [/productTypes]

Account-specific list of Product Types.

## Product Type Tasks Collection [/productTypesTasks]

Client-defined list of tasks to be tracked when processing any products in a given Product Type.

## Products Collection [/products]

Products produced by the account and assigned to specified Product Type.

